" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>We will do 1:1 video calls with everyone who want to learn more about skincare and what is best for their skin type and concern. Do you want to know more about it? Visit our Personal Skincare Advice page <span style="text-decoration: underline;">here</span> and schedule an appointment! Now let's start to answer some questions!</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1693206864417" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1693206864417" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1693206864448" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1693206864448" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1693206864395" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1693206864395"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">How did you first get into skincare?</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1693206864402" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1693206864402"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>I myself used to suffer a lot from <span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);">acne</span> and I could not find a solution for this. This is why I was searching for an answer by myself. I soon realised that my breakouts wouldn’t just go away over time. This started my journey for better skin, where I spent hours reading articles and watching videos that explained everything about the skin and all kinds of ingredients. I soon found out that I actually found this very interesting, and so I started studying it! I get super excited about skincare and love guiding others on their journey to their best skin possible!</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1681988158602" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681988158602" style="float: none; marg