px;" data-position="3"><u style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22);">Heartleaf 77% Soothing Toner</u></a><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">. I really can't decide between these two products, I’m sorry, okay!</span></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><strong>TIA'M - My Signature C Source</strong></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">In the TIA'M My Signature C Source there is<span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.49);"> Vitamin C</span> and f</font><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">or me, Vitamin C is my fave ingredient.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">It's great for your skin because it has some awesome benefits:</span></p><p><br></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"></font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1692776134938" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1692776134938" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692776134968" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1692776134968" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">1. <strong>Fights signs of ageing:</strong> It helps reduce wrinkles and keep your skin looking firm and youthful.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">2.<strong> Brightens skin tone: </strong>Vitamin C can fade dark spots and even out your complexion for a radiant glow.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">3. <strong>Protects against sun damage: </strong>While it's not a replacement for sunscreen, Vitamin C can give your skin some extra</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">defence against harmful UV rays.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">4. <strong>Speeds up healing:</strong> It helps heal wounds and fade acne scars by promoting the growth of new skin cells.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">5. <strong>Soothes inflammation: </strong>If you have acne, redness, or sensitive skin, Vitamin C can help calm things down.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">6. <strong>Improves texture: </strong>Regular use of Vitamin C can make your skin smoother and softer by getting rid of dead skin cells.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">Just make sure to choose a good Vitamin C serum or cream with a stable formula, and don't forget to wear sunscreen too! Your skin will thank you.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"></font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1692776134943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1692776134943" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><strong>Anua - Heartleaf 77% Soothing Toner</strong></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">Let’s now talk about the Heartleaf 77% Soothing Toner! This product was really the best for my acne prone skin. If you’re suffering from <span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);">redness, acne, and closed comedones</span>, this may be your S.O.S skin saver. For me, it worked very well for my inflammations and 