it; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Ingredients that can address hyperpigmentation are:</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• Vitamin C</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• Niacinamide</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• Retinol</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• AHA/BHA</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• Most important: Sunscreen&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1692773139847" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1692773139847" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1692773139875" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1692773139875" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-